    <li>
      <p>Todos os direitos reservados de Caio Maximus</p>
      <p>Dados recebidos de <a href="https://www.pokemon.com/br/pokedex/" target="_blank">Pokedex.com</a></p>
    </li>
      <li id="link"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/caio-maximus-047826231" target="_blank"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a></li>
      <li id="git"><a href="https://github.com/caiomaximusjs" target="_blank"><i class="bi bi-github" ></i></a></li>

    
  </ul>
</footer>
<script src="/script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
